title: Emperor of Solo Play
description: Emperor of Solo Play Manhwa The launch of the virtual reality game Warlord in the year 2035 changed the world. Ahn Jaehyun was one of many who sought to change his fate within it. But the price of devoting his entire life to the game was betrayal by the very comrades he trusted the most. Having lost everything because of that betrayal, Jaehyun is given one more chance to start over. “I’m never playing with others again. Whether I win or lose, I’ll do it all on my own, and show them exactly what that means.” While others roll dice to split the loot, Jaehyun is the one who takes it all for himself. And so begins his thrilling, ruthless, solo-kill gaming life! 솔플의 제왕, The King of Solo play, The King of Soloplay
